description: Serving as one of part of a highly successful 55 concession trailer team, Dan’s Deli Grill 46 is dishing out delicious comfort classics like hot dogs, sandwiches, gyros, sausages, and more throughout Central Ohio. These made-to-order meals are perfectly accessible, affordable, and delectable. For your next party, be sure to provide your guests with their next amazing food fix with Dan’s Deli Grill 46.
name: Dan's Deli Grill 46
